OL,4,Cwhile off-duty
OL,6,FA police officer who raped a woman at
OL,7,Fhis Devon home has been jailed.
OL,9,FPC Stuart Mines, 49, was off-duty when
OL,10,Fthe attack took place at his home in
OL,11,FDevon in October 2022.
OL,13,FHe had met the woman online, on a
OL,14,Fdating website.
OL,16,FFollowing his conviction by a jury
OL,17,Ffollowing a trial at Exeter Crown
OL,18,FCourt, he was sacked by Devon and
OL,19,FCornwall Police after more than 20
OL,20,Fyears of service.
