OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement, the
OL,7,Fwoman said she had suffered severe
OL,8,Fmental trauma following the rape and
OL,9,Fhad been unable to work as a result.
OL,11,F"Emotionally, I've been a total wreck.
OL,12,FI've spent endless nights unable to
OL,13,Fsleep, feeling worthless and violated
OL,14,Fby the actions of this horrid person,"
OL,15,Fshe told the court.
