OL,3,CPolice officer jailed for raping woman
OL,4,Cwhile off-duty
OL,6,F"Mines has ripped my confidence away.
OL,7,FEvery time I hear a police siren, see
OL,8,Fa police car or a police officer, it
OL,9,Fhas triggered panic and nausea, and
OL,10,Fhas been and still is a constant
OL,11,Freminder of what he has done.
OL,13,F"He completely destroyed my faith in
OL,14,Fmen and the police force.
OL,16,F"As a man, he should have been
OL,17,Ftrustworthy, law-abiding and morally
OL,18,Frespectful to women. He was none of
OL,19,Fthese.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
