OL,3,CPolice officer jailed for raping woman
OL,4,Cwhile off-duty
OL,6,F"The media coverage of the trial
OL,7,Fverdict meant that the people he was
OL,8,Fplaced alongside on that wing realised
OL,9,Fhe was a police officer, now a former
OL,10,Fpolice officer.
OL,12,F"That identification has led to extra
OL,13,Fproblems that have been managed
OL,14,Fsuccessfully by the prison but
OL,15,Fcontinue to have to be managed because
OL,16,Fof threats and comments."
OL,18,FJailing Mines for eight years, Judge
OL,19,FStephen Climie said he had "torn
OL,20,Fapart" his victim's life and said the
OL,21,Fattack had caused her significant harm.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@YO]{D@\OU|D@FO]
