OL,3,CPolice officer jailed for raping woman
OL,4,Cwhile off-duty
OL,6,F"I have considered very carefully the
OL,7,Fextent to which the offence of rape
OL,8,Fwas the primary trigger for many of
OL,9,Fthe issues which are detailed in her
OL,10,Fvictim personal statement," he said.
OL,12,F"In my judgment, having watched and
OL,13,Flistened to her, I am satisfied that
OL,14,Fthe impact of this event can be
OL,15,Fdescribed as severe, some might go so
OL,16,Ffar as to say even extreme."
OL,18,FThe judge said the offence was
OL,19,Faggravated by the fact Mines was a
OL,20,Fserving police officer at the time.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]tD@AOUxD@\O]
