OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F437A1743779182
OL,3,CPolice officer jailed for raping woman
OL,4,Cwhile off-duty
OL,6,F"It is aggravated to an extent by
OL,7,Fvirtue of the fact that you as a
OL,8,Fserving police officer at that time
OL,9,Fcould and should have been somebody
OL,10,Fwho, and I quote your victim, were
OL,11,Fcapable of being described as somebody
OL,12,Fwith integrity, respect, empathy,
OL,13,Fcourage, fairness and accountability,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,16,F"In respect of accountability, you are
OL,17,Fnow being held to account.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@fO]xD@AOU
