OL,3,CPolice officer jailed for raping woman
OL,4,Cwhile off-duty
OL,6,F"In respect of other matters, I make
OL,7,Fit clear that, as with any walk in
OL,8,Flife, there may well be a bad apple or
OL,9,Ftwo within any given profession who as
OL,10,Fa result of their behaviour, attach a
OL,11,Fdegree of blame to others within that
OL,12,Frole.
OL,14,F"Your conviction should not, in my
OL,15,Fjudgment, in any way, shape or form,
OL,16,Fimpact upon the integrity of the
OL,17,Fpolice generally, least of all, the
OL,18,FDevon Cornwall Constabulary, who do
OL,19,Foperate appropriately with integrity,
OL,20,Frespect, empathy, courage and
OL,21,Ffairness."
